name: Shreya Rao
summary: Shreya Rao is a 32-year-old South Asian woman living in Los Angeles, California. She's a software engineer in the technology industry, having graduated from the University of California, Berkeley. Shreya is fluent in English and Hindi. Compassionate, honest, and valuing knowledge and family, she loves coding, cooking, reading, running, and traveling. Shreya is a Hindu, politically liberal, and looking for a life partner in monogamous relationship. She doesn't have children currently, but wants to in the future. Shreya doesn't own any pets. She's a Virgo and an INTJ. Healthy living is important for her as she doesn't drink, smoke or do drugs, and maintains an active exercise regime. Shreya is particularly interested in a male partner aged 30-45, who doesn't have children but is open to having them, lives a healthy lifestyle, and matches her active exercise routines.
